Package net.smartcosmos.objects.model.extension Description

Defines a plugin metaphor whereby 3rd party developers can tap into an account's contextual data in order to perform advanced computations that are not natively supported by the SnapBundle platform. The primary means of near real-time integration with these external components is via an EventType notification delivered to an INotificationEndpoint managed by the extension.
